Sir, I plead with you to bring them back for a fair trial.

235
00:14:11,540 --> 00:14:13,120
不必审判了
There's no need for a trial.

236
00:14:13,460 --> 00:14:15,510
这是我们仅有唯一的机会
This is our one and only opportunity

237
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:18,860
能阻止他们企图带来的大规模死亡
to avert the great death that they intend for us.

238
00:14:18,860 --> 00:14:23,760
我没得选择  巫师今晚必须死
I have no choice in this. The witch will die tonight.

239
00:14:45,190 --> 00:14:46,670
这个地方存在多久了
How long has this been here?

240
00:14:47,460 --> 00:14:48,900
自我建成这房子之日
Since I built the house.

241
00:14:51,610 --> 00:14:53,590
除非你学会找个真正的藏身之所
You do not survive all that I have survived

242
00:14:53,590 --> 00:14:56,630
否则你的历练还是比不上我
without knowing how to keep a true hiding place.

243
00:14:57,100 --> 00:15:00,400
这间屋子  只有血印可以开启
This room, whose door only blood can open,

244
00:15:01,560 --> 00:15:03,140
这是我们的避难所
is our sanctuary.

245
00:15:03,140 --> 00:15:04,360
你在这里很安全
You'll be safe here.

246
00:15:04,860 --> 00:15:06,560
我们得在这里待多久
How long must we stay inside?

247
00:15:06,560 --> 00:15:09,350
至少一周  风才能吹净空气
I think at least a week before the winds cleanse the air.

248
00:15:10,940 --> 00:15:14,710
它能告诉我们什么时候开始
And this is how we will know it has begun.

249
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:18,520
外面有什么大难当头
What disaster unfolds outside

250
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:20,290
让我们必须得躲在这里
that we must cower from in here?

251
00:15:20,300 --> 00:15:24,090
今晚  塞勒姆附近会释放瘟疫
Tonight, there will be a plague released near Salem,

252
00:15:25,030 --> 00:15:27,200
瘟疫将降临清教徒的家
A pox upon the puritan house.

253
00:15:27,430 --> 00:15:30,670
只有体内流淌着巫师之血
Only those who carry the witch blood in their veins

254
00:15:30,670 --> 00:15:32,670
或是沾染到巫师之血的人
or are touched by it

255
00:15:32,670 --> 00:15:34,480
才能从瘟疫中幸存
will be safe from this pox.

256
00:15:37,050 --> 00:15:38,530
那我也会死掉
Then I will die of it, too.

257
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:43,820
柯顿·麦哲检查过  我不是巫师
Cotton Mather examined me. I'm no witch.

258
00:15:43,820 --> 00:15:44,640
真的吗
Really?

259
00:15:45,860 --> 00:15:48,470
那他作为一个巫师猎手
Then he is an even more incompetent witchfinder

260
00:15:48,470 --> 00:15:49,520
比我想像中更不称职
than I thought.

261
00:15:49,780 --> 00:15:53,140
四周看看  你认出什么来了吗
Look around. Don't you recognize anything here?

262
00:15:53,140 --> 00:15:55,610
你还很小的时候  我经常带你来这儿
When you were very little, I brought you here often,

263
00:15:55,610 --> 00:15:58,390
你生活的伊始并非是个该死的清教徒
that you might not begin your life as a damned puritan,

264
00:15:58,390 --> 00:16:00,600
无法聆听乐曲之声
without the sounds, the music in your ears,

265
00:16:00,610 --> 00:16:03,140
或是无法得见美术之彩的清教徒
or all the colors of art in your eyes.

266
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:04,230
这里
Here.

267
00:16:14,990 --> 00:16:17,060
这是你三岁的时候画的
You drew that when you were 3.

268
00:16:25,310 --> 00:16:26,270
这个
This.

269
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:31,380
这是你的最爱
Well, that was your favorite.

270
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:33,430
我雕给你的
I carved it for you.

271
00:16:35,370 --> 00:16:39,010
