It's the luckiest night of your life.

285
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:43,960
你不会知道你离毁灭有多近
You'll never know how close you all came to utter destruction.

286
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:48,640
你曾夺走了我所有重要的东西
You once took away from me everything that meant anything.

287
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:53,470
今晚  我终于能将其全部夺回
But tonight, I shall finally have it all back.

288
00:17:54,200 --> 00:17:55,870
你说的一点没错
Truer than you know...

289
00:17:59,540 --> 00:18:00,620
小姐
...mistress.

290
00:18:02,170 --> 00:18:04,690
你来干什么  叛徒
What do you want here, traitor?

291
00:18:05,730 --> 00:18:07,060
我  叛徒
I? Traitor?

292
00:18:07,750 --> 00:18:09,440
我忍受了那个变态
I, who have endured the worst

293
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:14,050
施加给我的无数痛苦  只为了保护你
That sick man could inflict upon my flesh to protect you?

294
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:15,860
我可不这么认为
I think not.

295
00:18:16,460 --> 00:18:19,120
是你背叛了那些养育过你的人
'tis you who have betrayed those who nurtured you,

296
00:18:19,120 --> 00:18:20,400
你背弃了这么多年来
You who have turned your back

297
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:23,390
我们苦心计划的一切
On everything we have planned these long years.

298
00:18:23,390 --> 00:18:24,150
不
No.

299
00:18:24,560 --> 00:18:27,050
我离开不是为了背叛  而是为了...
No, I'm leaving not to betray, but to be true...

300
00:18:27,460 --> 00:18:30,950
可能是此生头一次...做回我自己
Perhaps for the first time... to myself.

301
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:33,850
你哪也不准去
You are going nowhere.

302
00:18:39,070 --> 00:18:43,140
七年前  两个女孩走入了树林
Seven years ago, two girls walked into the woods.

303
00:18:43,140 --> 00:18:45,190
在那里  其中一人许下誓言
There, one of them made a vow.

304
00:18:45,190 --> 00:18:48,900
为封印那个誓言  她奉献了最为宝贵的东西
To seal that vow, she offered up a most precious thing...

305
00:18:49,440 --> 00:18:51,070
她腹中的小生命
The life she carried within.

306
00:18:51,650 --> 00:18:53,690
不用提醒我那个黑暗的夜晚
No need to remind me of that dark night.

307
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:55,630
我永远无法将它从记忆中抹除
I shall never be free of its memory.

308
00:18:55,630 --> 00:18:56,360
不
No.

309
00:18:56,700 --> 00:18:59,610
你不可能忘记自己根本没有全然了解的事
You cannot forget what you have never really known.

310
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:03,370
你就没问过自己
Have you never asked yourself,

311
00:19:03,370 --> 00:19:06,540
没怀疑过那晚真正发生了什么
Never wondered what really happened that night,

312
00:19:06,540 --> 00:19:09,270
没想过你腹中的生命到底去哪了吗
Where the life that swelled your belly went?

313
00:19:11,210 --> 00:19:12,940
那晚没有诞生
Nothing is created.

314
00:19:12,940 --> 00:19:14,460
也没有毁灭
Nothing is destroyed.

315
00:19:15,100 --> 00:19:17,910
一切只是转化而已
All is only ever transformed.

316
00:19:19,770 --> 00:19:20,800
打开吧
Open it.

317
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:45,420
我的孩子
My child...

318
00:19:48,210 --> 00:19:49,070
还活着
lives?

319
00:19:49,770 --> 00:19:53,740
目前还活着  看你怎么选了
For now, depending on your choice.

320
00:19:55,800 --> 00:19:59,030
这  这只是个为了控制我的邪恶诡计
This... this is some foul trick in order to control me.

321
00:19:59,030 --> 00:20:01,530
不  那晚你并没杀死那个孩子
No, you did not kill the child that night.

322
00:20:02,150 --> 00:20:05,320
