But when it is done, I swear to you, you will pay.

336
00:20:52,190 --> 00:20:54,990
我们都别无选择  玛丽
We must all live without choices, Mary.

337
00:20:55,890 --> 00:20:57,470
你应该最有体会
You know that best of all.

338
00:21:19,050 --> 00:21:20,090
他不见了
He's gone.

339
00:21:22,010 --> 00:21:23,670
奥登上尉不见了
Captain Alden's missing.

340
00:21:26,670 --> 00:21:27,590
是你干的吗
Was it you?

341
00:21:28,210 --> 00:21:30,110
我说过我不会让他被绞死
I told you I would not let him hang.

342
00:21:30,780 --> 00:21:32,560
谢谢  玛丽
Thank you, Mary.

343
00:21:34,210 --> 00:21:35,160
谢谢
Thank you.

344
00:21:42,300 --> 00:21:43,490
真美
It's beautiful.

345
00:21:44,540 --> 00:21:47,120
是啊
Yes. It is.

346
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:50,650
这是什么
What is it?

347
00:21:50,650 --> 00:21:51,490
死亡
Death.

348
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:55,670
